task.summary: Added interfaces representing customer database and payment system
Added default implementations of the database and billing systems (wrappers around CustomerDatabase and PaymentsSystem), refactored code to use them instead of concrete classes.
Fixed test for TravelTracker; added custom hamcrest matcher for checking, if object is contained in a list
Refactored test utilities into separate package
